{"tid":387711,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Big Big Channel 搞FIFA比賽　馮盈盈密操：秘訣係揀我愛隊阿仙奴","createTime":"2017-09-05T00:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T13:31:30.000Z","uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4370b88aed01e8f5a774be1364609e39c86bc6d","tid":387711,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:34:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/娛樂/108765/Big-Big-Channel-搞FIFA比賽-馮盈盈密操-秘訣係揀我愛隊阿仙奴\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F108765%2FBig-Big-Channel-%E6%90%9EFIFA%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD-%E9%A6%AE%E7%9B%88%E7%9B%88%E5%AF%86%E6%93%8D-%E7%A7%98%E8%A8%A3%E4%BF%82%E6%8F%80%E6%88%91%E6%84%9B%E9%9A%8A%E9%98%BF%E4%BB%99%E5%A5%B4&d=T6xoQvd6NSR2GGzZF4vtHcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=8500870c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/娛樂/108765/Big-Big-Channel-搞FIFA比賽-馮盈盈密操-秘訣係揀我愛隊阿仙奴</a><br />\n<br />\nBig Big Channel 搞FIFA比賽　馮盈盈密操：秘訣係揀我愛隊阿仙奴<br />\n<br />\n最近TVB力谷Big Big Channel，除了一班藝員不停開live同fans互動之外，仲開發一個娛樂專區，搞搞新活動，已知的活動包括有「明星麻將王大賽」和「明星Game超聯大賽」。就在早幾日，「明星Game超聯大賽」亦正式開打，這個活動其實就是兩個藝人一齊坐低打足球遊戲Fifa，繼早前麥美恩5比0大勝陳貝兒，昨晚又有張曦雯悶和王卓淇，而第三戰今晚就會在BBC開戰，會有麥凱程對許家傑。據知今次比賽會由男女分為紅、藍兩色，每組4人，總共4組，女子組分別為麥美恩、陳貝兒、簡淑兒和朱智賢為一組，另一組為張曦雯、王卓淇、馮盈盈和鄧佩儀，勝出的兩名就可以晉級。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要反馮了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce06fac9805dc2aaf11fcb173f94923b492729d","tid":387711,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc09bbb8a1b61da0a6f9c3859c43ff9c09773e15","tid":387711,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:21:02.000Z","msg":"阿狗女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157456e897f2e9c66ac0dae3df590509bebc2743","tid":387711,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite